<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>Get Credit Tokens</title>
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../assets/PhygitalifyQR icon.png">
        <link rel='stylesheet' href='stylesheets/style.css' />
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="/javascripts/scripts_token.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="header">
            <div>
                <img src="" alt="logo"><label>PhygitalifyQR</label>
            </div>
            <div>
                You: <label><%= walletAddress %></label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h1>Get Credit Tokens</h1>
        <div class="PQRFaucetArea">
            <div>
                <img src="" alt="icon">
                <h3>PQR Token Faucet</h3>
                <p>Dripping 10 PQR per day.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="resultMsg" id="resultMsg">
                <label>You got 10 PQR tokens!</label>
            </div>
            <div>
                <button id="setTrustlineBtn">Set Trustline</button><br/>
                <button id="claimTokensBtn">Claim tokens</button>
                <p>You'll receive up to 10 PQR daily but the total number of boosts available will never exceed 10. For instance, if a you have 7 boosts, you'll only receive 3 more boosts. If you run out of PQR, you have the option to get additional PQR tokens from XRP.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="exchangeArea">
            <h3>Exchange PQR for XRP</h3>
            Coming Soon
        </div>
    </body>
</html>